platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Dont know your contrast from your saturation? This app makes photo editing approachable, letting you make adjustments (and save them as presets) with a few taps. Its a simple but powerful way to freshen up your snaps.

Si vous ne savez pas diffrencier le contraste et la saturation, cette app rend plus accessible la retouche photo en vous permettant en quelques gestes de procder  des ajustements (et de les enregistrer comme modles). Cest une manire simple et efficace de donner une seconde vie  vos clichs.

Looking for a simple but powerful way to freshen up your photos? Photomator makes editing approachable even if you dont know your contrast from your saturation. With a few taps, the app lets you adjust specific color ranges, perfect your photos shadows, and fix up highlights. And once youve found settings you like, save them as your own presets.
